reviewText: Does the actually rock and roller stepper come with DVD or is this just to buy the DVD
This is good but wanted more music!
friend has one and lost 50lbs along with diet. I need to lose weight and exercise so this is convenient and equipment easy to store

The item is fine and shipping was speedy but I am not 21 and I thought this was exercise to rock and roll music not a rock and roll machine I would fall off. For someone that has this machine it would be perfect.
